<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT89">
<l>paḻutākā toṉṟaṟintēṉ pāṟkaṭalāṉ pātam</l>
<l>vaḻuvā vakaiṉiṉaintu vaikaṟ ṟoḻuvārai</l>
<l>kaṇṭiṟaiñci vāḻvār kalanta viṉaikeṭuttu</l>
<l>viṇtiṟantu vīṟṟiruppār mikku.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have learned of one [means] that is unfailing:</l>
<l>Those who live seeing and bowing down to the people</l>
<l rend="indent">who unerringly meditate upon and worship [all] day</l>
<l rend="indent">the feet of [the Lord] on the milky ocean</l>
<l>shall overcome the karman intertwined [with their souls],</l>
<l>open Heaven and sit high with distinction [there].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
